items.badge_description: Fifth in our series of “Super Style” badges, this one is dedicated to the beloved Imperial IPA, which ranked as the [3rd most checked-in style of 2021](https://untappd.com/blog/the-top-10-styles-of-2021/1390). AVAILABLE ONLY TO UNTAPPD INSIDERS

When a single isn’t enough, make it a double. Doubling the hops and malts in a recipe results in a higher ABV and can pack quite a boozey punch. That's 415 different beers with the style that contains Imperial / Double in its style name. Try 5 more for Level 84!
